<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ب ص ص:</span> <span class="c2">(الْبَصِيصُ)</span> الْبَرِيقُ وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(بَصَّ)</span> الشَّيْءُ لَمَعَ يَبِصُّ بِالْكَسْرِ <span class="c2">(بَصِيصًا)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(بَصْبَصَ)</span> الْكَلْبُ وَ <span class="c2">(تَبَصْبَصَ)</span> أَيْ حَرَّكَ ذَنَبَهُ وَ <span class="c2">(التَّبَصْبُصُ)</span> التَّمَلُّقُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>